<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>New Sign-In Detected</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: #f4f6f9; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #1a1a2e; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 600px; margin: 32px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%); padding: 36px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; color: #fff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.3px; }
    .header p { margin: 8px 0 0; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); font-size: 14px; }
    .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .body { padding: 36px 40px; }
    .greeting { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .intro { color: #555; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .info-card { background: #fefce8; border: 1px solid #fde68a; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .info-card h3 { margin: 0 0 14px; font-size: 13px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.8px; color: #92400e; font-weight: 700; }
    .info-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #fde68a; font-size: 14px; }
    .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .info-label { color: #78716c; font-weight: 500; min-width: 110px; }
    .info-value { color: #1c1917; font-weight: 600; text-align: right; word-break: break-word; }
    .reasons-section { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .reasons-section h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #b45309; }
    .reason-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 8px 12px; background: #fff7ed; border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 14px; color: #44403c; }
    .cta-section { text-align: center; margin: 28px 0; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 15px; color: #555; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-confirm { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background: #16a34a; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; }
    .btn-revoke  { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background: #dc2626; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 600; }
    .warning-box { background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; font-size: 14px; color: #b91c1c; margin-bottom: 24px; line-height: 1.5; }
    .footer { background: #f8fafc; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
    .footer p { margin: 0; font-size: 12px; color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; }
    .footer a { color: #6366f1; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="icon">🔐</div>
      <h1>New Sign-In Detected</h1>
      <p>Was this you? Please confirm or revoke access.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <div class="greeting">Hi {{displayName}},</div>
      <p class="intro">
        We detected a sign-in to your MeriGauMata account that looks different from your
        usual pattern. Review the details below and take action.
      </p>

      <div class="info-card">
        <h3>Sign-In Details</h3>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Time</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{signedInAt}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">IP Address</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{ipAddress}}</span>
        </div>
        {{#if city}}
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Location</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{city}}{{#if region}}, {{region}}{{/if}} ({{country}})</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Device</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{deviceType}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">OS</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{os}} {{osVersion}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="info-row">
          <span class="info-label">Browser</span>
          <span class="info-value">{{browser}} {{browserVersion}}</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      {{#if suspicionReasons}}
      <div class="reasons-section">
        <h3>Why we flagged this sign-in:</h3>
        {{#each suspicionReasons}}
        <div class="reason-item">⚠️ {{this}}</div>
        {{/each}}
      </div>
      {{/if}}

      <div class="cta-section">
        <p>If this was you, trust this device. If not, revoke access immediately.</p>
        <div class="btn-row">
          <a href="{{confirmUrl}}" class="btn-confirm">✅ This was me</a>
          <a href="{{revokeUrl}}" class="btn-revoke">🚫 This wasn't me</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="warning-box">
        ⚡ If you did not sign in, click "This wasn't me" immediately and change your
        password at <a href="{{secureUrl}}">{{secureUrl}}</a>.
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>
        This email was sent by MeriGauMata · <a href="{{frontendUrl}}">merigaumata.com</a><br/>
        You're receiving this because unusual sign-in activity was detected on your account.<br/>
        © {{year}} MeriGauMata. All rights reserved.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
